15
00:01:24,709 --> 00:01:26,043
Jung Goo Yeong?

16
00:01:26,044 --> 00:01:29,546
Goo Yeong was on the mountain when Da Won got lost.

17
00:01:29,547 --> 00:01:31,173
Did you see Da Won?

18
00:01:31,174 --> 00:01:33,325
He could've easily got the commander's gloves into his hand.

19
00:01:33,325 --> 00:01:35,469
Take Goo Yeong in?

20
00:01:35,470 --> 00:01:36,929
We must take him ourselves.

21
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:39,707
The day Da Won went missing. Why did you go there?

22
00:01:39,707 --> 00:01:41,475
I had things to do.

23
00:01:41,476 --> 00:01:44,770
All the victims had something to do with the mountain.

24
00:01:44,771 --> 00:01:47,231
Why are they all together?

25
00:01:47,231 --> 00:01:50,860
[5:16 pm - Hikers, an old man and his wife, three college students in their twenties; Volunteer Fire Squad Cho Il Man, Lee Jong Goo, Kim Jin Deok. Residents Seo Young Jin, Yoon Soo Mi.]

26
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:52,595
All the victims...

