30
00:01:58,951 --> 00:02:03,606
Hyun Jo knew who the murderer was.

31
00:02:03,606 --> 00:02:07,918
Did Hyun Jo tell you anything before the accident on the snowy mountain?

32
00:02:07,918 --> 00:02:09,987
After that incident last summer,

33
00:02:09,987 --> 00:02:12,072
I haven't been able to see him.

34
00:02:12,072 --> 00:02:13,867
Last summer...

35
00:02:13,867 --> 00:02:16,736
A lot of painful things happened.

36
