[Jirisan National Park Haedong Ranger Station]

37
00:02:57,930 --> 00:02:59,420
[Gwigam Rock]

38
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:01,347
Gwigam Rock.

39
00:03:05,393 --> 00:03:08,421
Are you here because of that?

40
00:03:09,939 --> 00:03:11,565
Or...

41
00:03:11,566 --> 00:03:13,993
