[96 mm]

60
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:16,184
Get out of the valley! Hurry!

61
00:07:16,185 --> 00:07:20,298
Quick! Leave the valley!

62
00:07:20,298 --> 00:07:23,183
Please move! Move!

63
