There's no time! We must leave!

68
00:08:58,871 --> 00:08:59,913
Over there!

69
00:08:59,914 --> 00:09:02,041
Quick!

70
00:09:02,041 --> 00:09:04,209
Leave right now!

71
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:06,920
Get the children out!

72
00:09:07,755 --> 00:09:10,132
You must leave now!

73
00:09:10,132 --> 00:09:12,634
We don't have time.

74
00:09:15,731 --> 00:09:18,932
We don't have much time. Hurry!

75
00:09:26,774 --> 00:09:28,693
Not much time left!

76
00:09:28,693 --> 00:09:29,901
Let's move!

77
