I repeat.

81
00:09:39,787 --> 00:09:42,914
There has been localized heavy rain on Jirisan.

82
00:09:42,915 --> 00:09:46,167
Residents near the valleys and streams,

83
00:09:46,168 --> 00:09:48,487
please take caution.

84
