[Caution: Falling Rocks]

86
00:10:21,370 --> 00:10:22,388
Here, here! Wait for a second!

87
00:10:22,388 --> 00:10:23,814
Wait up!

88
00:10:23,814 --> 00:10:26,216
It's dangerous here!

89
00:10:26,216 --> 00:10:28,800
Go back!

90
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:42,370
[Jirisan National Park Haedong Station]

91
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:58,265
